esource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salisbury\", \"score\": 0.9936637012827105, \"rank\": 0.006374604475822337, \"text\": \"Salisbury\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salisbury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salisbury\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999794039178677, \"rank\": 1.6803972232111253e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her first-round win over Stephens in Eastbourne, Raducanu cited her eagerness to avoid the reoccurrence of past injury issues as her reason to reject an Olympics spot.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"score\": 0.999999997474788, \"rank\": 1.9612029713925606e-09, \"text\": \"Eastbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think at one point I was chasing, playing too many tournaments when I wasn't ready,\\\" Raducanu explained after her victory against Stephens.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then I was just picking up niggle after niggle in every tournament because I never really gave myself any time to do the training and the work.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's something I did a lot better this year.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even though I might get challenged or questioned for not playing certain tournaments like the French Open or the Olympics, I think that for me, that is just part of